data.description: This is the one you've been looking for!! All you have to do is Move In!! Located on a dead-end cul-de-sac, this 2-story colonial home has a spacious open floor plan with/ over 2,000 sq ft. The living room features a gas fireplace & custom built-in shelving. The kitchen has an abundance of solid wood cabinets, a convenient pantry, ample counter space for food prep or entertaining & a sit-up breakfast bar area! A formal dining area, breakfast nook, 1/2 bath & laundry area complete this level. Upstairs are 4 spacious bedrooms & 2 full bathrooms. The master bathroom has a walk-in shower & a large walk-in closet. Step outside into the fully fenced-in backyard. Relax & enjoy the outdoors from your pergola w/ bistro lighting & firepit. 1 Car garage and an attached carport for extra parking & storage. This popular model will not last long!
